{"tid":1496634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲墨爾本香港人全部同我入嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:53:30.000Z","uid":276681,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1eba7e832267eed50dbdffb851385d881d49d92d","tid":1496634,"uid":276681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"我哋係一群住係墨爾本關心香港嘅香港人，因為知道何韻詩下個禮拜會喺悉尼演講，冇理由冇墨爾本份㗎嘛!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我哋岩岩運用外國勢力, 好辛苦先係何韻詩嘅檔期裏面<strong>R</strong>左9月4號一晚，地點待定！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望支持呢位香港親善大使繼續幫手喺海外遍地開花。<br />\n我哋亦正盡力邀請其他澳洲重要人物及國際傳媒，希望可以喺海外一齊兄弟爬山！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為時間緊迫好需要大家眾籌支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/be-water-vs-sharp-power?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fbe-water-vs-sharp-power%3Futm_source%3Dcustomer%26utm_medium%3Dcopy_link%26utm_campaign%3Dp_cp%2Bshare-sheet&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=e318a25d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/be-water-vs-sharp-power?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet</a><br />\n<br />\n由何韻詩聯同中澳政治漫畫家巴丟草先生 (Badiucao) 一同探討當前香港面對的危機與未來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKfiyu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKfiyu7.jpg&h=1f893ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴丟草都好勁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E8%A2%AB-ig-%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E5%85%BC%E6%8E%A5%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%B0%E8%A6%8B%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%9F%E8%8D%89%E6%96%A5%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25A2%25AB-ig-%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%25B0%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E4%25B8%259F%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%2596%25A5%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=87ecbfec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25A2%25AB-ig-%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2585%25BC%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%259A%2587-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%25B0%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E4%25B8%259F%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%2596%25A5%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&h=c9fb30a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E8%A2%AB-ig-%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E5%85%BC%E6%8E%A5%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%B0%E8%A6%8B%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%9F%E8%8D%89%E6%96%A5%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/badiucao-fears-storm-is-coming-after-revealing-identity-on-tiananmen-anniversary?language=zh-hant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fbadiucao-fears-storm-is-coming-after-revealing-identity-on-tiananmen-anniversary%3Flanguage%3Dzh-hant&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=e52f7014\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/badiucao-fears-storm-is-coming-after-revealing-identity-on-tiananmen-anniversary?language=zh-hant</a><br />\n<br />\n墨爾本香港人全部義務支持，活動結束後我們將扣除一切開支，將經費餘款全數撥捐予「 612人道主義救濟基金」<br />\n<br />\nSend 比所有關心香港嘅澳洲人同香港人!!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返一個半星期!! 幫手推唔該！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df98a3edc29be0e9c3604098f20eb0e9ca53cf8","tid":1496634,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"Portland street 街坊表示支持"},{"pid":"ca4b88d824bfd0ab0cdd1a54d38864feb733f044","tid":1496634,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf